"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-06-26-jessica-ennis-hill-backs-katarina-johnson-thompson-end-olympic-heartache-paris-2024-21101918\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Dame Jessica Ennis-Hill believes Katarina Johnson-Thompson can finally banish her Olympic heartbreak and claim gold inParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Olympic heartbreak\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"gold inParis\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's reigning heptathlon world champion hobbled out of theTokyo Gamesthree years ago midway through the competition with a calf injury, having only just been fit to compete there after recovering from rupturing her Achilles.\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9881751801479804, \"rank\": 0.011965943545588288, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999999998094609, \"rank\": 1.9035561293482339e-10, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"a calf injury\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Injury concerns once again overshadow Johnson-Thompson's preparations for thisOlympics, with the 31-year-old having pulled out of the European Championships earlier this month after three events because of an issue with her right leg.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Injury concerns\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"overshadow\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson's preparations\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"thisOlympics\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"the European Championships\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"an issue\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"her right leg\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It appears, though, she will be fit to compete in Paris andLondon 2012winner Ennis-Hill believes Johnson-Thompson, who despite all her success has never won an Olympic medal, can follow in her footsteps to the top of the podium and defeat Belgian's two-time champion Nafi Thiam.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3463481463937998e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7402336437132074, \"rank\": 0.2067421070646, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ennis-Hill\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"all her success\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"her footsteps\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I strongly believe Katarina is the one to watch as I definitely think she has it in her to bring home gold,' Ennis-Hill told Metro at the launch ofEurostar's first Golden Train, which will transport athletes and fans between London and Paris.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.643387974947595e-12, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999977477175788, \"rank\": 2.193004490633887e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3463481463937998e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"Ennis-Hill\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"the launch ofEurostar's first Golden Train\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is the fourth time she has been in the Olympics and because she is so experienced, she has a lot to bring to the event.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fourth time\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately she has had a lot of disappointment in the previous Olympics but Katarina has been here so many times before and knows what it takes to win.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.643387974947595e-12, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous Olympics\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She will really want to put her previous issues aside.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her previous issues\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very confident she will turn it around and be victorious.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'As for her fitness, she looks in really good shape but it's going to be a tough one as she has Nafi Thiam to contend with, as well as American Anna Hall.\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1616, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997505396779558, \"rank\": 0.0001413555429201407, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\", \"score\": 0.999999191157585, \"rank\": 8.088230647854918e-07, \"text\": \"Anna Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Hall_Roosevelt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fitness\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"really good shape\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough one\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That being said, Katarina has the right tools now to get that gold.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.643387974947595e-12, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right tools\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Her mindset is excellent and that is an important part of being a winner.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her mindset\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"a winner\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her focus is now right on track; she seems relaxed and happy, and that means she will perform her best.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her focus\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You never know what's going to happen in a heptathlon though but I think this is the time Katarina is going to smash it.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heptathlon\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"Katarina\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there is ever a time, it is now.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am totally backing her.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently when I have seen her compete she is so consistent and determined and if she can bring that into the Olympics, then she's got every chance of winning.'\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"every chance\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as KJT, Ennis-Hill is confident Team GB will be celebrating numerous medals, pointing to the likes of reigning 1500metres world champion Josh Kerr, sprinter Dina Asher-Smith and 800m star Keely Hodgkinson, who she acknowledges is 'one of the gold-medal favourites'.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2311, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.959012757915111e-18, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 2467, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"KJT\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"Ennis-Hill\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous medals\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"1500metres\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"800m star\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold-medal favourites\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Dina's chances of winning a medal are very high and I am excited to watch her compete,' she added.\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dina's chances\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Indoor pole vault champion Molly Caudery can do well too.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"score\": 0.999995872758395, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Molly Caudery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Caudery\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is one of the newest and brightest stars in British athletics and can win a medal.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.980197098269791, \"rank\": 0.012519107629073468, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the newest and brightest stars\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She is at the top of her game.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"her game\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really looking forward to watching her.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After working as a BBC commentator for the 2020 Olympics, Ennis-Hall is looking forward to being a part of the Paris Games, where - as well as taking to the stage for a live Q&A - she will join sport and entertainment presenters Nick Bright, Nicole Holliday and Perri Shakes-Drayton who will be hosting a nightly live show.\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2891, \"end\": 2894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9998025369361266, \"rank\": 0.0001974147799522601, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Bright\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Bright\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Bright\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Bright\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"Ennis-Hall\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"a live Q&A\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicole Holliday\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"Perri\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"Shakes-Drayton\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"a nightly live show\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is going to be a totally different experience to Tokyo when I was a commentator for the games and was confined to a studio in Manchester because of Covid restrictions,' Ennis-Hill told Metro.\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3252, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9789447383766187, \"rank\": 0.021508115235728514, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3329, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999993910933, \"rank\": 6.000119272730972e-10, \"text\": \"Manchester\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped